Package com.banking.cs213project3

package com.banking.cs213project3
  • Class
    Description
    Account
    This is an abstract class which extends in to subclasses that have account information for the various accounts.
    AccountDatabase
    AccountDatabase holds different accounts in an array and implements operations to grow, find, close, open, withdraw, deposit and print information for the accounts.
    Campus
    Enum representing the possible campuses for the CollegeChecking account
    Checking
    The checking class extends the account class and implements monthly interest rates and fees for this type of account
    CollegeChecking
    CollegeChecking class specifies the monthly interest and fees associated with this type of account.
    Date
    An instance of this class holds a date Provides multiple methods that check if a date follows criteria to be considered valid
    MoneyMarket
    MoneyMarket class extends Savings and defines a type of account with monthly interest and fees depending on the loyalty and balance of the customer.
    Profile
    The profile class specifies the name and date of birth for a given account.
    Savings
    Savings class specifies the monthly interest and fees associated with this type of account.
    TransactionManagerController
    Controller for the JavaFX GUI
    TransactionManagerMain
    Main Class to launch the GUI
